Quand Munna mange un rve, celui-ci
est aussitt oubli par le rveur.
Il lvite en permanence.

Munna always float in the air. People
whose dreams are eaten by them
forget what the dreams had been about.

Il se nourrit des rves des gens et des
Pokmon. Quand le rve est agrable,
il crache une fume rose.

It eats the dreams of people and
Pokmon. When it eats a pleasant
dream, it expels pink-colored mist.

This Pokmon appears before people
and Pokmon who are having nightmares
and eats those dreams.

and Pokmon who are having nightmares
and eats those dreams.

Il apparat aux humains et aux Pokmon qui font
des mauvais rves et mange leurs cauchemars pour
les en librer.

Es erscheint vor schlafenden Menschen
und Pokmon und frisst ihre Alptrume.

Cuando un humano o un Pokmon sufre una pesadilla,
Munna se aparece ante ellos y la engulle.

Compare accanto a Pokmon e uomini tormentati
dagli incubi per nutrirsi di tutti i loro brutti sogni.

Tief in der Nacht erscheint es am Kopfende von
Betten. Whrend es einen Traum frisst, schimmert

Aparece en plena noche junto a la almohada

motivos de su cuerpo emiten una luz tenue.

Appare vicino al guanciale nel cuore della notte.

corpo si illuminano lievemente.

Late at night, it appears beside peoples pillows.
As it feeds on dreams, the patterns on its body
give off a faint glow.

Il se nourrit de songes et expire de la fume

ou noire sil sagit dun cauchemar.

Whrend es Trume frisst, stt es Dunst aus.
Bei frhlichen Trumen ist dieser rosafarben,

El humo que despide cambia de color en funcin

rosa, o negruzco en el caso de una pesadilla.

Si nutre di sogni. Esala un fumo rosa se sono
sogni piacevoli e nero se sono incubi.

It eats dreams and releases mist. The mist is pink
when its eating a good dream, and black when
its eating a nightmare.
